# Stress test: increase CPS in steps while injecting server delay at peak.
# Takes snapshots before and after for comparison via traffic_summary.
#
# Usage:
#   tools/events-schedule.sh tools/events-schedule-examples/stress-test.driver

Timeline(s)   cps:myFlow   vault:RESPONSE_DELAY_MS   snapshot
0             0            0              baseline
5             500          0              -
60            1000         0              -
120           2000         0              peak-no-delay
180           2000         100            peak-with-delay
240           2000         500            peak-high-delay
300           0            0              final
